Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.57,0:00:05.22,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be together anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:11.99,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Shione!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:13.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:19.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work together, \Nlike way back when.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.97,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We're all waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:25.21,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We can do it, the five of us together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:32.57,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:08.48,sora-ep-title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,440)}The Meaning of Goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:08.89,sora-main-top,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, did something \Nhappen with Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:14.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were friends again yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.90,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'd work on it with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:22.74,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is Togawa holding onto something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:26.03,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:27.50,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.22,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:31.00,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Shione's just being shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.10,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:35.98,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to be with us, \Nbut she's too embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:38.60,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:40.63,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,She told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:48.05,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "Do you like \NNonoka or not? Tell me."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.44,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you asked that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:56.96,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What did Shione say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:03:01.45,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,"Of course."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:04.58,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,So don't be discouraged, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:07.23,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:08.94,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:12.54,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I trust Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.47,Festival,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hokubi Festival Invitation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:24.40,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:26.97,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:30.22,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, aren't you with \NNonoka and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.66,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, there's something \NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.23,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:39.54,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What happens to the saucer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:41.74,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,once you grant our wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:46.82,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Once I grant your wish, I get \Ncalled over to another wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.50,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Just like when you all called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:52.48,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:57.50,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,"Saucer-san, saucer-san, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:01.54,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,grant my wish."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:06.50,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Your wish is going to be granted soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.26,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:10.00,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:17.27,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, are you leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:21.09,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to see the planetarium, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:30.86,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:32.66,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.67,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:36.69,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.41,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I want a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:42.39,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But is the saucer going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.17,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:47.55,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to see the planetarium, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:50.33,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel and Shione...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:54.71,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's going to smile now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:57.06,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:18.60,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hoping to go to the Hokubi \NFestival on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.15,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,How are preparations going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:21.75,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We're a little behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.34,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We have three days to \Ndo something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:25.51,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.44,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:29.97,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:31.72,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:33.47,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.98,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:37.51,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:38.19,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.14,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.19,sora-main,Q,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu came crying to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:46.09,sora-main,Q,0000,0000,0000,,She's was all, "We won't make it in time."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.92,sora-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You're here for the rice cakes, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:52.11,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that we need the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.44,sora-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You should have asked sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:57.16,sora-main,O,0000,0000,0000,,We need more than four \Npeople to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.98,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we can get it \Ndone on time now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.17,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:06.22,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,How are you supposed to know what \Nto do if I don't give orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.54,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:09.94,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need your \Norders to do our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.18,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Get busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:13.25,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:16.59,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, I'm sure Shione is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:18.40,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:20.31,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:25.39,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,She gave a Hokubi Festival ticket \Nto Noel, just like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.39,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So I trust
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.24,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.19,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make this a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.00,sora-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.00,sora-overlap,All,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:41.12,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:45.00,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:48.71,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you need \Nto worry about, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:52.89,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to get there \Nas soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.93,thisway - Copy,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,350)}Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.21,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.33,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I know I said I wanted to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.31,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.08,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it snowed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:54.31,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.50,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Time really flew by.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:08:00.04,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Shione's coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.00,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.76,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:07.54,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, once we're all here, \Nit'll be like the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:11.95,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We'll celebrate with \NKoharu's rice cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.30,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:23.21,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Close the door. I can see everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:25.81,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Souta, come here, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:27.81,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:29.28,Signs,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Planetarium This Way                    Planetarium on Display
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:32.04,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.58,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:38.03,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking, \Nyour hobby's turning out to be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:40.54,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:45.21,Closed,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Closed for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:53.19,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:57.01,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need about this many.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:08.02,Book,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1600)}Mysterious Supernatural Encyclopedia
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:09.65,Book2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1750,1)}How to Call a Flying Saucer (UFO)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.86,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:21.86,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,No one takes me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:24.19,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You believe it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.00,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:27.92,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Then I do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:32.54,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:37.13,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I bet we're not the only ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.51,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two talking \Nabout so secretly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.02,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:48.40,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Help me call a saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:50.72,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:54.53,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:56.89,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A saucer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.26,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be awesome, \Nif one actually came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.28,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone would be amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.79,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We might end up on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:05.82,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:06.88,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.21,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:29.23,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,For Koharu, Yuzuki and Souta to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:31.98,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,And Shione, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.45,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,That was their wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:43.23,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:45.81,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's too easy. No fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:50.47,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more thing we need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.63,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,When we call the saucer,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:56.10,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,we have to think about \Nsomething we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.38,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,A wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:02.98,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,The saucer is supposed to be attracted \Nto our strong feelings that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:07.21,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,So we have to make a wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:10.64,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean the saucer \Nwill grant it for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:13.00,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:15.41,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but what if we have a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.12,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Just pick one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:19.83,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.42,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:22.66,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.77,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I already have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:27.36,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:28.16,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:33.07,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It might not come true if I told someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.25,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:46.20,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Saucer-san, saucer-san, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.90,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,grant my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.29,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.67,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.34,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.00,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.54,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.69,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I promised to meet her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.84,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.30,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.59,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:24.88,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.39,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:46.28,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,The saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:49.24,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:08.30,thisway - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12}Hokubi \NMiddle School
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:08.30,School,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14}The Melody We \NWant to Share with You
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:14.56,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:23.44,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, can you show Noel-chan around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.02,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:27.86,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Leave all this stuff to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:31.48,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you as soon as we find Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:32.44,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:34.29,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go around school with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.32,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:38.29,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:44.80,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It smells so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:46.93,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.43,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:49.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:50.73,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.04,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:54.93,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,That!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.43,Soup,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Red Bean Soup
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.80,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It's so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.01,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:13.01,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.23,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:26.51,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It really is sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:27.87,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:32.30,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a red bean bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:35.49,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It's sweet, but it's \Nall so warm and tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:37.98,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.98,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Nonoka, where's Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:57.00,sora-main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fs18}Frankfurters                                     Fried Chicken
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.57,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,She should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:48.75,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,She might be at the planetarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:53.14,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go meet up with Yuzuki and \Nthe others when we're done eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:54.30,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:57.00,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.50,thisway,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Planetarium \NThis Way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.50,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The planetarium is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.50,Planet,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Planetarium
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:01.50,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:04.05,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:05.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:08.16,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,She's still not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:09.58,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.12,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.64,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The Hokubi Festival's just starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:15.93,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.55,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:20.21,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Good, Komiya's here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.12,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard from the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.31,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa's absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.72,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.57,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:32.57,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Shione's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.22,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where she lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.60,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:38.29,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:40.79,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be okay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:41.96,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.66,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:52.22,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to see the planetarium \Nwhile we're waiting for Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:55.22,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see it with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:57.15,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.18,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:01.63,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.64,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:08.90,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:11.03,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,To my friend's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.42,Planet2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Planetarium
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:27.42,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:31.04,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:33.67,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:38.93,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, it's because you're \Ncarrying that thing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.43,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You should text her Togawa's address.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:48.18,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Where was I going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:54.65,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:16:59.16,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:04.03,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:09.50,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:12.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I saw her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:13.77,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:16.51,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look for her a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.38,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:37.03,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:48.32,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you \Nnot to come near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.97,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you coming \Nto the Hokubi Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.63,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.74,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:57.32,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you not understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:18:00.67,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't want to be with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:04.72,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not coming because \Nyou can't forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:11.26,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you can't forgive me after \NI made you wait seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:14.61,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But Shione, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.37,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You must be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:20.25,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I don't want to \Nhear what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:23.13,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,So stop talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.27,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel's waiting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:30.75,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You gave her the ticket because \Nyou wanted to see it with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.37,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:39.52,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I want us all to see the \Nplanetarium together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:41.39,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,The meteor shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:44.32,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I want us to have fun \Ntogether like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:47.65,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,To talk and laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:49.00,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:18:58.83,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.91,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:05.10,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Stop using my given \Nname like we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:06.24,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Use it again, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.37,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.94,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to call you Togawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:18.55,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.09,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:26.06,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,...hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:27.82,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:29.31,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Or hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:32.06,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't friends or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.79,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,How can I smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.27,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:40.49,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Because Noel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:52.14,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:54.70,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I don't make promises I can't keep,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.49,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't say things \Nto get people's hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:01.87,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Komiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.60,sora-main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fs16}Buttered Potatoes                                               Fried Noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:26.16,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Nonoka found Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:30.41,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, there's no point to this if \Nthe five of us aren't all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:32.54,sora-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to help clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:35.82,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, we'll do it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:38.42,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the cleanup to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.57,sora-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:43.48,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:44.93,sora-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,No, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:52.60,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't given up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.44,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.31,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, where's Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.29,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,She was there a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.99,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she went after Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:05.73,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:07.56,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:33.92,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:35.64,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:39.64,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:43.11,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:47.45,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.87,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
